Michael D. Siegal 
Executive Compensation
As Chairman & Chief Executive Officer at OLYMPIC STEEL INC, Michael D. Siegal  made $953,984 in total compensation.  Of this total $750,000 was received as a salary, $0 was received as a bonus, $0 was received in stock options, $42,468 was awarded as stock and $161,516 came from other types of compensation. This information is according to proxy statements filed for the 2016 fiscal year. 


