Accessible & Reliable New York Attorneys
Serving you with integrity and respect At Siegel & Siegel, P.C., we are a husband and wife practicing law together.  We were both trained and practiced for many years at large law firms.  It is our firm's mission to combine large firm quality with personal attention and care for clients and their problems.  If you have a legal problem, call us and let our family help you and your family. Our attorneys strive to provide creative and strategic legal solutions that ensure that our legal fees are the best investment for you and your family. At Siegel & Siegel, we help clients formulate and then handle the day-to-day administration of complex estates and trusts. In our bankruptcy practice, we counsel you on the true impact of bankruptcy and will fight to ensure you have a fresh start, free from debt and creditors. Siegel & Siegel, P.C. regularly handles: Trusts & estates Bankruptcy Commercial litigation Real estate Workable solutions that fit your needs We take care of your money as if it were our own. Our attorneys approach your situation from multiple angles to ensure we maximize your chance of success in achieving your goals. When you retain Siegel & Siegel, P.C., you can expect us to tailor our solutions to your particular needs and objectives. Contact a respected New York law firm today Call Siegel & Siegel, P.C. at 212-721-5300 or contact us online to schedule an appointment. 
 Siegel & Siegel, P.C. serves clients in New York City (Manhattan, Brooklyn, Queens, Bronx and Staten Island) and Nassau, Suffolk, Westchester, Rockland and Dutchess counties.  Our New Jersey office serves Bergen, Hudson, Essex, Monmouth, Ocean and Morris counties.  
 






